html
	head
		meta(charset='UTF-8')
		meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1')
		title Karol Świerczek - Portfolio
		link(rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css")
	body
		.menu.menu--transparent
			.menu__logo 
				p Karol Świerczek
			.menu__buttons
				.menu__button Home
				.menu__button About me
				.menu__button My portfolio
				.menu__button Offer
				.menu__button Contact
		.heading
			.heading__stack.float
				img(src='images/stack.svg' height='700px')
			.heading__about
				h1 Karol Świerczek
				p I'm 17 years old web developer from Cracow and I'm keen on building modern, minimalistic websites. My dream is to work as a front-end developer and I'm doing my best to make it real.
		.intro
			.intro__slot
				.intro__title About me
				p I've been programming since I was 12 years old and web development has always been my passion. I esspecially love to make one-page websites because I can concentrate on design, but more advanced projects are also welcome. 
			.intro__slot
				.intro__title My workflow
				p Every single website which I've made is unique because I'm not using any templates and ready-made patterns. I'm constantly developing my skills because I want to deliver the highest quality product to the customer.
		.portfolio
			.portfolio__background
				img(src='images/background2.svg')
			.portfolio__title My portfolio
			#projects.portfolio__projects
				.project(v-for='project in projects')
					.project__desc
						.project__photo
							img(:src='project.image')
						a.project__title(target='_blank' :href='project.url') {{project.title}}
						.project__about {{project.about}}
						.project__annotation {{project.annotation}}
			script(src='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/vue/2.5.3/vue.min.js')
			script(src='js/index.js')